Maintainer: Mike Cheng <mikefc@coolbutuseless.com>
URL: https://github.com/coolbutuseless/picosatire
BugReports: https://github.com/coolbutuseless/picosatire/issues
Description: A solver for Boolean satisfiability problems ('SAT') using the
    'PicoSAT' library.  For this solver, 'SAT' problems can be formulated in 
    two ways; using integer literals, or using logical expressions 
    specified with the 'satire' package.
